# Document System Phase 4 Task Checklist

## 1. Timeline & Template Versioning Logic
- [x] Timeline Default Times & Spanning:
  - [x] Adjust Timeline to start from a further point in the past/future and allow year-based or infinite ranges (null vs exact date logic).
  - [x] Default start time applied to 00:00, end time to 23:59.
- [x] Timeline Auto-Adjustment (Collision Handling):
  - [x] If a user edits a timeline block and it overlaps another, crop the existing blocks rather than rejecting the save.
- [x] TemplateBuilder Save Flow:
  - [x] Add explicit "Save over current version (vX)" vs "Save as New Version" buttons.

